{"id": "art-2702e", "label": "Art. 2702e)", "title": "Art. 2702e)", "slug": "art-2702e", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_509495113\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1110\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_509495113\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 270<sup>2e)</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2014971713\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1109\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2014971713\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> care nu au\nvotat în favoarea hot&#259;rârii adun&#259;rii generale prin care a fost\naprobat transferul sediului într-un alt stat membru au dreptul de a se retrage\ndin societate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de a solicita cump&#259;rarea <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span> lor de c&#259;tre societate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_150347247\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1108\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_150347247\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dreptul de retragere poate fi exercitat în termen de 30\nde zile de la data adopt&#259;rii hot&#259;rârii adun&#259;rii generale.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_135383632\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1107\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_135383632\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Ac&#355;ionarii</span> vor depune la\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, al&#259;turi de <span\nclass=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> scris&#259; de retragere, <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> pe care le posed&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, certificatele\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1891268586\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1106\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1891268586\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Pre&#355;ul</span> pl&#259;tit de\nsocietate pentru <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> celui ce\nexercit&#259; dreptul de retragere va fi stabilit de un expert autorizat\nindependent, ca valoare medie ce rezult&#259; din aplicarea a cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> dou&#259; metode de evaluare recunoscute de <span\nclass=SpellE>legisla&#355;ia</span> în vigoare la data evalu&#259;rii. Expertul\neste numit de registratorul de registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>,\nîn conformitate cu <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 38 <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 39. Costurile de evaluare vor fi suportate de\nsocietate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1176625899\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1105\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1176625899\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Registratorul de registrul <span class=SpellE>comertului</span>,\nulterior verific&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ntransferului, <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;&#259;</span> o încheiere ce\natest&#259; îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span>\nprev&#259;zute de art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>3</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>-</span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>5</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din prezenta <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a celor prev&#259;zute de art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>8</span><span style='color:black'> din Regulamentul\nConsiliului (CE) nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>2.157/2001</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_371881619\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1104\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_371881619\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Ulterior radierii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\neuropene transferate, oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\nva comunica Jurnalului Uniunii Europene, pe cheltuiala <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nun <span class=SpellE>anun&#355;</span> privind radierea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndin registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> din România ca urmare a\ntransferului sediului acestuia într-un alt stat membru.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>TITLUL <span class=SpellE>VIII:Contraven&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span></span></b></p>"}